item.title: Rs-remake release
item.dc:creator: @Fridder Fridder
item.description:
@Fridder wrote:

Crysis_v2:

Lets just hope this is clean, and not filled with viruses.

Moparisthebest:

First thing is first, I downloaded the archive, and while I can’t be sure it’s not a virus, I extracted it, it does indeed include java source code and class files (most of the archive is the cache), and it does NOT contain any .exe, or .bat files, it contains a single run.cmd file that just runs java and is not malicious. So it probably isn’t a virus and doesn’t contain one, of course always scan and verify things yourself though. . . So no, this won’t be removed since it doesn’t appear to be malicious.
